item.title: How to change these? Look in!
item.dc:creator: @crimsonbow13 crimsonbow13
item.description:
@crimsonbow13 wrote:

Well, thats probably considered a shop. So I would go into Shops.CFG and search for the Void ID,
Then look for the ‘200’ which would be the price, and change it to what you want. No need to compile afterwards, you don’t need to with CFG files. Just do that, save. Runserver.

GL to ya ;]
